A silent virtual microphone for macOS that keeps your AirPods in full audio quality.

## Install

```bash
brew install --cask timschmolka/tap/hush
```

Prefer building from source? `brew install --formula timschmolka/tap/hush`.
Then choose **Hush** in System Settings → Sound → Input.

## Verify the download

This installer is signed with a Developer ID and notarized by Apple, so Gatekeeper
accepts it without warnings:

```
spctl -a -vvv -t install __PKG__
# → accepted / source=Notarized Developer ID
```

SHA-256 (also in `SHA256SUMS.txt`):

```
__SHA__  __PKG__
```
